{"tid":872092,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【實戰理論】美股勢危 反彈有限（沈振盈）（22/10）","createTime":"2018-10-22T12:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T12:43:11.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b3639705729bf24f71017e6958c254bb6855ef40","tid":872092,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:27:02.000Z","msg":"週末期間金融市場沒有太多的消息，美股上週五晚走勢亦喘定，但要留意着三大指數接着而來的趨勢。道指下破26000點之後，雖然在25000關口前初步喘定，並展開反彈，但反彈力度只是一般。若然再下破25200的支持，則跌穿24800的機會頗大。由於美股的基本面向淡，估值太高、盈利增長前景向淡，配合現時的技術動力欠佳，估計道指會最終回試23000點水平，而此水平是美股牛市的最後防線。除道指之外，標普500指數及納斯達克指數的情況，就更加惡劣。納指已確認見頂，終極防線7200點，現在距離此水平已不遠。<br />\n<br />\n至於港股方面，去週先跌後反彈，但始終未能重上26000點之上，形成了底部的橫行區。由於外圍走勢欠佳，多項負面消息不斷輪流發酵，下跌趨勢頗難逆轉。<span style=\"color: red;\">暫時估計波幅區間介乎25000-26200點，若下破25000點的話，有機會出現另外的一千點跌幅。</span><br />\n<br />\n而內地股方在三大巨頭出面維穩之下，才能出現反彈。然而，筆者覺得這只是形式上出口述，令到A股的跌勢放緩而已，<span style=\"color: red;\">始終不跌不跌還須跌，上証2500點仍未有足夠的支持力</span>，去完成今次熊市跌浪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.winmoney.hk/famous/%E3%80%90%E5%AF%A6%E6%88%B0%E7%90%86%E8%AB%96%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E5%8B%A2%E5%8D%B1-%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%EF%BC%88%E6%B2%88%E6%8C%AF%E7%9B%88%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%882210%EF%BC%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.winmoney.hk%2Ffamous%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25AB%2596%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%258B%25A2%25E5%258D%25B1-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2599%2590%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%25B2%2588%25E6%258C%25AF%25E7%259B%2588%25EF%25BC%2589%25EF%25BC%25882210%25EF%25BC%2589%2F&d=84eQHd2i79vBtAkCGwBTQ9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=81ebaa52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.winmoney.hk/famous/%E3%80%90%E5%AF%A6%E6%88%B0%E7%90%86%E8%AB%96%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E5%8B%A2%E5%8D%B1-%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%EF%BC%88%E6%B2%88%E6%8C%AF%E7%9B%88%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%882210%EF%BC%89/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 師父"},{"pid":"80605e7c182711829d0a3cf80b60a9a17937b113","tid":872092,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:28:28.000Z","msg":"反彈浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f491dd49eb80b65c0d49b0fc09251d7341c84b","tid":872092,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80605e7c182711829d0a3cf80b60a9a17937b113","tid":872092,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:28:28.000Z","msg":"反彈浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:30:00.000Z","msg":"師傅屌打習大"},{"pid":"47d98a288102d41434623feb66ac0bb52f9145f3","tid":872092,"uid":204245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買返10 張大期g持"},{"pid":"5b3d25d88fca2b58ba7e59adbd69471d68f890a8","tid":872092,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"富途六週年 壕撒股票雨<a href=\"https://j.futunn.com/001JYC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.futunn.com%2F001JYC&d=84eQHd2i79vBtAkCGwBTQ9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=529b9a5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://j.futunn.com/001JYC</a><br />\n<br />\n祝大家股票贏到開巷<br />\n買乜都賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces